The Adventures of Superman #608-609
Publisher:  DC Comics
Publication Date:  September 11, 2002 and October 9, 2002

Writer:  Joe Casey
Artist:  Derec Aucoin
Colorist:  Rob Ro and Alex Bleyaert
Letterer:  Comicraft
Cover:  Kevin Nowlan

The Adventures of Superman #608
"Ending Battle" part 2, continued from Superman v2 #186. The inexplicable attacks on Superman's friends and family continue, as Atomic Skull arrives at the Kent farm. Meanwhile, a host of super-villains start attacking people associated with Clark's childhood in Smallville. Continued in Superman: The Man of Steel #130.

The Adventures of Superman #609
"Ending Battle" part 6, continued from Superman v2 #187. On the trail of the man responsible for the attacks on his friends and family, Superman is attacked by an armada of new villains. Can the Man of Steel stand up to the sheer number of adversaries against him? Continued in Superman: The Man of Steel #131.
